Package: statquiz
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Statistics Practice in the R IDE
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chayce", "Reed",
        email = "code.jcr@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit for practicing statistics interactively inside the
    R environment. Generates randomized questions across topics including
    ANOVA, Welch's ANOVA, t-tests, non-parametric tests, correlation,
    simple linear regression, chi-square, Fisher's exact test, probability,
    and scenario-based test selection. Students solve questions using
    standard R functions and check their answers with immediate feedback.
    Includes a quiz mode for scored multi-question sessions, per-topic
    hints, and worked-solution explanations.
